                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "usp_VoucherBillsByInvoiceBillingGroup",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " call fails, the procedure does not capture or log the error, which could lead to silent failures."
